rdfs:label: dateTimeClass
dc:description: Date-times should conform to ISO8601 date-time format YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss. Any variation on the full form is allowed.

rdfs:label: nameClass
dc:description: Value class designating values that have the characteristics of node names. The allowed characters are alphanumeric, hyphen, and underbar.

rdfs:label: numericClass
Attributes: allowedCharacter=digits, allowedCharacter=E, allowedCharacter=e, allowedCharacter=+, allowedCharacter=-, allowedCharacter=.
dc:description: Value must be a valid numerical value.

rdfs:label: textClass
Attributes: allowedCharacter=letters, allowedCharacter=digits, allowedCharacter=blank, allowedCharacter=+, allowedCharacter=-, allowedCharacter=:, allowedCharacter=;, allowedCharacter=., allowedCharacter=/, allowedCharacter=(, allowedCharacter=), allowedCharacter=?, allowedCharacter=*, allowedCharacter=%, allowedCharacter=$, allowedCharacter=@
dc:description: Value class designating values that have the characteristics of text such as in descriptions.
